          <title>No. 10 Alabama escapes Auburn with a 27-20 victory thanks to Simpson-Horton connection</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Ty Simpson and Isaiah Horton connected three times for touchdowns, including on a fourth-down play in the waning minutes, and No. 10 Alabama escaped Auburn with a 27-20 victory in the rivalry known as the Iron Bowl on Saturday night.]]></description>
